        1.3.6 (2014-12-08)
        ------------------
        
        - BugFix: Pass email_from as string, not as email.header instance.
          This fixes sending emails with an Exchange.
          [mathias.leimgruber]
        
        - Do not show invite link, if internal user and email invitation is disabled.
          [mathias.leimgruber]
        
        
