        ------------------
        
        - Participants: fix table layout for read-only users.
          [jone]
        
        - Participants: hide users without roles.
          This can happen when inheriting the Owner, because inherited Owner
          roles are removed.
          [jone]
        
        
        1.3.3 (2014-08-07)
